ActExport Development Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for International Trade of DONALD A. MacLEOD of Bedford, Nova Scotia, as a director of the Board of Directors of Export Development Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of J. Bernard Boudreau.
